<h1 align="center" id="title">FTC Deployment App</h1>

<p id="description">This app is designed to streamline and automate the FTC deployment process at YKB. Currently the deployment is managed manually using notebooks and pens followed by entering the data into a Google Sheet. This method is both time-consuming and monotonous. To address these inefficiencies I developed this app. It eliminates the need for repetitive manual entry making the deployment process faster and more efficient. With this solution we can save time reduce errors and improve overall productivity.</p>
